I just checked that spares_transpose function seems to work fine without any error even for sparse tensor of order/rank >5, unlike what you previously stated.

I tested this on build # 234 (last stable build on cpu only macosx)

Could you or someone please clarify if sparse_transpose function is correctly implemented for sparse tensors of rank greater than 5? Thanks.
